spec_data.Name: winswitch
spec_data.Description:
Application to start and control remote GUI sessions via xpra, NX,
VNC, RDP or plain ssh X11 forwarding.  Winswitch can start, suspend,
resume and send supported sessions to other clients.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 11:50:39 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Utility for controlling remote desktop sessions
